data.description: Nestled in the heart of Chesapeake, this cozy home offers the perfect blend of comfort, connivence  and elegance. The highlight of this home is the finished detached garage, thoughtfully designed to offer both independence and connection with its own kitchen, bath, washer & dryer hookups and unfinished upstairs to add more square footage as needed! A gorgeous renovated kitchen with new floors through out. So many updates have been done in the last 2 years. Renovated master bath with heated tile floors as well. This home sits on a huge corner lot with extensive landscaping just completed with water views!
